    "org_about":  "QatarDebate is a center under the Qatar Foundation in Qatar. It aims to promote the culture of debate in both Arabic and English among young people locally and internationally.\r\n\r\nThe center trains students in critical thinking, public speaking, and structured dialogue through training programs, workshops, and local and international debate tournaments. It also seeks to empower youth to express their opinions in a scientific and logical manner and to build a generation capable of effective discussion and positive influence in society.",
